The paper deals with a new multimodal retrieval task involving videos and subtitles, which suggests that it could belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) or natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper proposes a novel Cross-modal Moment Localization (XML) modular network, which could also place it in the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of different baselines and analysis experiments, which could suggest it belongs to the information retrieval (cs.IR) or machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
